          "الإنفاق": "Spending in charity and generosity",
          "الإمساك": "Withholding, retention -- the opposite of generosity",
          "الإقبال": "Worldly prosperity, when fortune approaches",
          "الإدبار": "Adversity, when fortune departs"
        },
        "seo_question": "What did Imam al-Sadiq say about stinginess and generosity?"
      },
